articles.title: It could take a decade for other automakers to catch Tesla — and none are 'leading contenders' just yet, experts say
articles.description: Though it's early in the days of EV adoption, automakers other than Tesla don't seem like they'll be able to catch up to Elon Musk in short time.
articles.content:
It's hard to gauge which automaker will be the runner up to Tesla in the coming years  and there might not be one at all.
